   110→### Precise time delta
   112→```pycon
   113→>>> import humanize
   114→>>> import datetime as dt
      →…
   124→#### Smaller units
   126→If seconds are too large, set `minimum_unit` to milliseconds or microseconds:
   127→
   128→```pycon
   129→>>> import humanize
   130→>>> import datetime as dt
   131→>>> humanize.naturaldelta(dt.timedelta(seconds=2))
   132→'2 seconds'
   133→```
   134→
   135→```pycon
   136→>>> delta = dt.timedelta(milliseconds=4)
   137→>>> humanize.naturaldelta(delta)
   138→'a moment'
   139→>>> humanize.naturaldelta(delta, minimum_unit="milliseconds")
   140→'4 milliseconds'
   141→>>> humanize.naturaldelta(delta, minimum_unit="microseconds")
   142→'4 milliseconds'
   143→```
   144→
   145→```pycon
   146→>>> humanize.naturaltime(delta)
   147→'now'
      →…
   154→### File size humanization
   156→```pycon
   157→>>> import humanize
   158→>>> humanize.naturalsize(1_000_000)
      →…
   166→### Human-readable floating point numbers
   168→```pycon
   169→>>> import humanize
   170→>>> humanize.fractional(1/3)
      →…
   182→### Scientific notation
   184→```pycon
   185→>>> import humanize
   186→>>> humanize.scientific(0.3)
      →…
   200→## Localization
   202→How to change locale at runtime:
   203→
   204→```pycon
   205→>>> import humanize
   206→>>> import datetime as dt
   207→>>> humanize.naturaltime(dt.timedelta(seconds=3))
   208→'3 seconds ago'
   209→>>> _t = humanize.i18n.activate("ru_RU")
   210→>>> humanize.naturaltime(dt.timedelta(seconds=3))
   211→'3 секунды назад'
   212→>>> humanize.i18n.deactivate()
   213→>>> humanize.naturaltime(dt.timedelta(seconds=3))
   214→'3 seconds ago'
   215→```
   216→
   217→You can pass additional parameter `path` to `activate` to specify a path to search
   218→locales in.
   219→
   220→```pycon
   221→>>> import humanize
   222→>>> humanize.i18n.activate("xx_XX")
   223→<...>
   224→FileNotFoundError: [Errno 2] No translation file found for domain: 'humanize'
   225→>>> humanize.i18n.activate("pt_BR", path="path/to/my/own/translation/")
   226→<gettext.GNUTranslations instance ...>
   227→```
   228→
